#### 3. File:`stats_models/src/lib.rs`:Line 702 – GLM summary uses simplified R-squared calculation

The `GlmFit::summary` method calculates R-squared using the residual sum of squares (RSS), which is more appropriate for linear models. For GLMs, a deviance-based pseudo-R-squared (`1 - deviance / null_deviance`) is standard practice. The current implementation is a reasonable simplification but lacks statistical rigor.

```rust
